(28, 1, '2015-01-15 04:17:22', '2015-01-15 04:17:22', 'Aloxo is a fully responsive WordPress theme built with the eCommerce functionality in mind. This is the most advanced and flexible theme we’ve built so far.\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/aloxo-responsive-woocommerce-theme/9994416\">Demo</a> | <a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/aloxo-responsive-woocommerce-theme/9994416?ref=samit9119\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">Download</span></a></strong></p>\r\n<a href=\"http://aztheme.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Aloxo-Responsive-WooCommerce-Theme.png\"><img class=\" size-full wp-image-29 aligncenter\" src=\"http://aztheme.net/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Aloxo-Responsive-WooCommerce-Theme.png\" alt=\"Aloxo - Responsive WooCommerce Theme\" width=\"590\" height=\"300\" /></a>\r\n<h3 id=\"item-description__features\">FEATURES</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>100% responsive:</strong> Built with HTML5 and CSS3 and 1170 pixel layout based on the Bootstrap 3.0 advanced Grid system, Alomo Theme adapts automatically to your tablets and mobile devices. Each an every element, including our awesome premium sliders are fully responsive, and it would allow your customers to browse the shop from any device.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Smart Products Ajax Search: </strong>Aloxo features a powerful Smart Products Ajax Search.Visitors can choose product category for search and display search results are also listed in a drop-down box on the go according to what visitors typed in the Search Box, and these results are all listed on the current page.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Unlimited Layout:</strong> With our customized shortcodes, you can create unlimited layout for your front page, post, page, Login page, and even Custom Post Type. You can create any layout you want. The only limit is your imagination.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Powerful Theme Options:</strong> Our awesome and advanced theme options allow users to customize Aloxo quickly and easily. Users can adjust the margins, change the color scheme or typography. Everything is grouped to one Theme Options menu for a quick and easy control.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Unlimited Colors &amp; Skins:</strong> You can change the layout, colors and styles, and customize your shop to the last corner. The flexibility nature of Aloxo will let you create shops with completely different display though they are all built from the same awesome Aloxo framework.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Advanced Typography Options:</strong> We’ve included 600+ Built-in Google fonts and 400 vector icons from Font to give you more choice in your customization for Aloxo. You can also change the font-size, font family and font-weight. In short, Aloxo will give full control on typography options.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Sticky Header:</strong> We’ve put a Sticky header that is visible at all time when users scroll your shop, to help your customers save time while browsing. The height of this Sticky Header can be controlled through the Theme Options, and you can freely choose whether to show it or hide it.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Slider Revolution ($19 value for free):</strong> This plugin creates responsive slideshows with customizable transition/ animation effects, while still keep or built your SEO optimization. With Aloxo, you will be saving $19 but can still benefit from tons of unique transition effects, an image preloader, video embedding, autoplay that stops on user interaction and lots of easy to set options.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Visual Composer ($30 value for free):</strong> Visual Composer for WordPress is drag and drop frontend and backend page builder plugin that will save you tons of time working on the site content. You will be able to take full control over your WordPress site, build any layout you can imagine – no programming knowledge required. Moreover, now you can choose either work on a backend or move your page building process to frontend and instantly see changes you make.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>WPML (Multilingual) Ready:</strong> The Aloxo Multipurpose WooCommerce WordPress Theme 100% compatible with the multilingual WPML plugin, allow you to built multiple languages WordPress site.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Boxed and Fullwidth Layout modes</strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong>Built-in Custom Widgets:</strong> Our beautiful and powerful widgets will let you display important elements on your sidebar by just dragging, dropping and some customization: • Aloxo Flickr • Aloxo Latest Blog • Aloxo Search on Page • Aloxo Social Links • Aloxo Twitter</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Testimonials:</strong> This Custom Post Type is created with places to include social network links to show off lovely feedbacks from your customers.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Custom background, 2 Logos &amp; Favicon:</strong> You can choose a color for your shop background, or you can upload an image to used as background for your shop to give it more atmosphere. Aloxo also supports 2 logos and one favicon that you can upload.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Custom Style:</strong> Need more customization? You can easily add custom CSS directly from our Theme Options Pagel without touching the core theme files. These styles will overwrite the theme style and will not be lost when users upgrade their Aloxo theme.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Unlimited Sidebars:</strong> Users can also create an unlimited number of sidebars without having to touch the function.php file, and set them to replace default sidebars in specific pages. You will be able to create custom sidebars with specific widgets that fit perfectly on your pages and posts.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Optimized for Speed:</strong> The clean design and well structured code of Aloxo ensures a 94% score on the page speed grade. Users can also disable features they are not using to increase the speed even more.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Shortcode Generator:</strong> The Shortcode Generator in our Content Editor allows users to build shortcodes quickly and easily to insert on any page. Shortcodes are elements that we use to build our Aloxo pages. Many of our shortcodes have several display options for users to choose. Optimized for SEO: Aloxo is built with SEO in mind. The way it allows search engines to index the content of your shop easily will help you get a high ranking on their result pages.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Contact Form 7 Plugins:</strong> Aloxo have a built-in contact form built with Mailchimp for WP. The layout of this form is customized to match the design of our demo shop. For more advanced forms, we supports the free Contact Form 7 plugins, and it will also be installed by default during the theme activation.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>100% Child Themes support:</strong> Allow you to modify the Aloxo theme without losing customized works when updating to newer version – which we will do frequently.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Demo Data:</strong> Users can easily setup a shop exactly like our demo site with the provided demo content that they can import. It would help new users to save more time and effort in setting up their shops using Wordpress framework and Aloxo.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Cross browser compatible:</strong> Aloxo support most of popular browsers and it will ensure that your shop looks go gorgeous in any environment. Clean and modern design: Aloxo offers a clean and modern pre- built layout that suit many product types and is able to give them the highlight they deserve.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Compatible with WooCommerce plugins:</strong> WooCommerce is the free Wordpress ecommerce plugin that is automatically installed with Aloxo theme activation.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Multiple payment options with Tax Calculator:</strong> The tax tab displays several options for your choose a configuration that suits your needs. Tax will be automatically calculated based on your shop location.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>User Accounts and Order Tracking:</strong> The WooCommerce Order Tracking Form shortcode will let an user see the status of an order by entering their order details.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Listing and Gridview in Shop page:</strong> You can make your product page display items in a timeline view with the Listing option, or in rows and colums with the Gridview option.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Shipping options:</strong> WooCommerce works with USPS, UPS or FedEx to ship your items. And the price will be auto calculated for you.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Coupon option:</strong> Coupons are a great way to offer discounts and rewards to your customers, plus they help promote sales across your WooCommerce shop.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Downloadable/Digital Products support:</strong> This option allows you to setup a shop that sell virtual products like ebooks or software licenses.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Product Sliders:</strong> These WooCommerce shortcodes enables you to embed slideshows of WooCommerce products, featuring best sellers products, featured products, top rated products, on sale products, or new arrival products.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Compare feature:</strong> The chosen products are compared side- by-side, feature by feature, price-by- price. Discard products from the table at the click of a mouse as you hone in on the product that is the one for you. You can save the comparison as a PDF or print it.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Wishlist feature:</strong> WooCommerce Wishlists allows guests and customers to create and add products to an unlimited number of Wishlists. From birthdays to weddings and everything in between, WooCommerce Wishlists are a welcome addition to any WooCommerce store.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Quickview feature:</strong> The quick view plugin adds a ‘quick view’ button to product loops which shows product details in a lightbox when clicked.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Share product feature:</strong> These social sharing buttons will let you show your product pages on various social network for internet marketing and advertisement. Detail page of the product with: • Multiple images for your product with slider and Zoom Effect • Related products, ratings and description tab.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Unlimited product variations option:</strong> This great feature of WooCommerce let shop owners offer variations of a product with different prices, stock and more. Variations of a product can be set e.g. a large t-shirt vs a small t-shirt. Each variation can have different properties and prices.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Custom checkout pages:</strong> This feature gives you a vast amount of capabilities to manage your products on checkout such as removing fields that you do not need, removing the required attribute rendering the field optional to customer or even perhaps adding more fields to the checkout page.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Frequent Updates:</strong> We promise to update the product frequently to keep it up-dated to the latest version of WordPress, WooCommerce plugin as well as other 3rd-party plugins.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>We care about customer support:</strong> Every support enquiry will be taken care within 24 hours in week days, normally within 12 hours on account of different timezone.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/aloxo-responsive-woocommerce-theme/9994416\">Demo</a> | <a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/aloxo-responsive-woocommerce-theme/9994416?ref=samit9119\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">Download</span></a></strong></p>', 'Aloxo - Responsive WooCommerce Theme Download full', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'aloxo-responsive-woocommerce-theme-download-full', '', '', '2015-01-15 04:17:22', '2015-01-15 04:17:22', '', 0, 'http://aztheme.net/?p=28', 0, 'post', '', 0),
