o data installation</li>\r\n	<li>Lightbox Integration for Images and videos</li>\r\n	<li>And Above of the all 100% free Customer Support</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://aperio.bradweb.net/\"><strong>Demo</strong></a> | <a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/aperio-multipurpose-wordpress-theme/9978573?ref=samit9119\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>Download</strong></span></a></p>', 'Aperio Multipurpose Wordpress Theme Full Download', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'aperio-multipurpose-wordpress-theme-full-download', '', '', '2015-01-17 04:40:41', '2015-01-17 04:40:41', '', 0, 'http://aztheme.net/?p=45', 0, 'post', '', 0),
